    • Method Detail

      • readProperties

        public static Stock readProperties()
                            throws CSVFormatException,
                                   StockException
        Read item_properties.csv, creates Items from each line of file, and fills a Stock object with Items. Each item will have a quantity equal to its reorder value. The returned Stock object is also stored within a private static variable accessible to all methods in this class.
        Returns:
        Stock object containing every Item in the item_properties.csv file, with a quantity equal to each Item's reorder amount.
        Throws:
        CSVFormatException - Thrown when error in opening or reading file occurs.
        StockException - Re-throws exceptions thrown by methods used within.

      • readManifest

        public static Manifest readManifest()
                             throws CSVFormatException,
                                    DeliveryException,
                                    StockException
        Reads the manifest.csv file, and creates a Manifest from this data. The Trucks contained in the Manifest each contain Stock with Items specified in the manifest file.
        Returns:
        A Manifest object containing a number of Trucks as specified by the manifest file.
        Throws:
        CSVFormatException - Exception thrown when the FileReader has trouble opening, closing, or reading the desired file.
        DeliveryException - Re-throws exceptions thrown by methods used within.
        StockException - Re-throws exceptions thrown by methods used within.

      • createItem

        private static Item createItem(java.lang.String line)
                        throws CSVFormatException,
                               StockException
        Creates an Item from properties saved to a single line of a CSV File, constructing a cold or dry item as necessary.
        Parameters:
        line - String containing entire contents of one line of a CSV file, including commas, but without newline characters
        Returns:
        An Item correlating to the properties contained within line. May be either temperature-controlled or dry Item.
        Throws:
        CSVFormatException - Exception caused by incorrect number of properties required to create Item.
        StockException - Re-throws exceptions thrown by methods used within.

      • closeReader

        private static void closeReader()
                         throws CSVFormatException

        Throws:
        CSVFormatException - Exception occurs when program fails to close file correctly.

      • getItem

        private static Item getItem(java.lang.String itemName)
        Searches through the stock generated from the item properties file to locate an Item object with a desired name.
        Parameters:
        itemName - String containing the desired item's name.
        Returns:
        Item with corresponding name to input String, null if no corresponding Item exists in Stock.

      • createTruck

        private static Truck createTruck(java.lang.String truckType,
                                 Stock contents)
                          throws DeliveryException,
                                 StockException
        Private helper method to create either a RefrigeratedTruck or OrdinaryTruck depending on input string.
        Parameters:
        truckType - String containing either "Ordinary" or "Refrigerated".
        contents - Stock object to reside in Truck.
        Returns:
        RefrigeratedTruck or OrdinaryTruck with contents inside.
        Throws:
        DeliveryException - Exception thrown when type of truck not recognized.
        StockException - Re-throws exceptions thrown by methods used within.
